  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "When the ork hordes of the warlord Snagrod, the Arch-Arsonist of Charadon, sweep through the sector, the Crimson Fists are first to answer, only to be all but annihilated. Worse follows on their home world of Rynn's World, where a single errant missile obliterates the Chapter's fortress-monastery and most of its warriors in an instant. With only a handful of battle-brothers left, Chapter Master Pedro Kantor and the indomitable Captain Cortez must wage a desperate planetary war from the ruins, holding the line at New Rynn City against a green tide that vastly outnumbers them. It is a fight not only for a world, but for the very survival of a proud Chapter teetering on the edge of extinction.",
